we need to talk about kevin is a 2011 british-american psychological thriller drama film directed by lynne ramsay , and adapted from lionel shriver 's novel of the same name .   a long process of development and financing began in 2005 , with filming commencing in april 2010 .   tilda swinton stars as the mother of kevin , struggling to come to terms with her son and the horrors he has committed .   the film premiered at the 2011 cannes film festival and was released in the united kingdom on 21 october 2011 .   swinton was nominated for the golden globe award , screen actors guild , and the bafta for best actress in a leading role .   it was given positive reviews by both critics and audiences alike .